        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Fifth Exception",
        "Location": "LOCATION_GOLDEN_GECKO",
        "PublicId": "127334764500",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/golden/mission_gecko/scene_gecko_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 76093a1e-fc60-4207-ae0c-91a2b6c4f226).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\n\nDubai’s skyline will serve as both stage and witness.\nYour targets are five individuals moving within this vertical city.\n\nFour deaths must be indistinguishable from accidents—\ninevitable, unnoticed, and without suspicion.\n\nThe fifth, however, is an exception.\nA deliberate act, delivered by your own hand.\n\nNo firearms. No unnecessary force.\nNo one must be subdued.\n\nLet the city decide four.\nYou will decide the last.\r\r\r3/2026",
